{"tid":760893,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[砌女] 新手求教","createTime":"2018-07-30T02:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T08:13:31.000Z","uid":162066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0a23fec49da2bdefa02cf6d31a9bed9b5bcd8690","tid":760893,"uid":162066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"小弟部機用左5年，差不多係時候換機<br />\n<br />\n換機既目標係想絲滑順暢咁打MHW同埋BF5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家個list大概就係 :<br />\n<br />\nCPU :  i7-8700<br />\n底板 :  B360 AORUS GAMING 3 WIFI<br />\ndisplay card : GTX1060 6GB (而家用緊)<br />\n火牛 : 550w (用緊)<br />\nHDD : ???<br />\n<br />\n想問下如果唔玩超頻，8700係咪抵玩過8700K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n底板個到，8700既話多數配B360,但B360都有成堆，唔識揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHHD有冇巴打可以推介D長壽唔易死既, 3TB夠玩了<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下SSD同RAM係電腦節先買會唔會抵買D？而家RAM價真係升得快過火箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該哂，咁多巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba97003bc2280f7f72ecda6bc08cd8e2ec40800d","tid":760893,"uid":60622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:03:29.000Z","msg":"老母板揀塊插頭位置唔好奇奇怪怪嘅就得<br />\n<br />\n即係裝落個機箱之後啲風扇呀乜撚野果啲線夠長插到就得<br />\n<br />\n反正b系列板都係屎唔使買貴野<br />\n<br />\n在座咁多位都係垃圾.jpg"},{"pid":"5afa100874e50ebcc0264134538b156f71aec545","tid":760893,"uid":59734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"想耐用D就研究下底版D  VRM 設計 唔好貪平<br />\n尤其用一體水又無風吹底板版heatsink"},{"pid":"9715c15de756fcfb6b7caa29ba3b9f474bad54bb","tid":760893,"uid":162066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5afa100874e50ebcc0264134538b156f71aec545","tid":760893,"uid":59734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"想耐用D就研究下底版D  VRM 設計 唔好貪平<br />\n尤其用一體水又無風吹底板版heatsink"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"Small potato未玩過水冷，有必要上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8e8854fae43dbc6d94816ef8a3cc3a4b5c645b","tid":760893,"uid":59734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9715c15de756fcfb6b7caa29ba3b9f474bad54bb","tid":760893,"uid":162066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5afa100874e50ebcc0264134538b156f71aec545","tid":760893,"uid":59734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"想耐用D就研究下底版D  VRM 設計 唔好貪平<br />\n尤其用一體水又無風吹底板版heatsink"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"Small potato未玩過水冷，有必要上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:18:04.000Z","msg":"其實唔駛，不過要確保連塊版都要有風吹到"},{"pid":"a56123c82fecca920a43c130cc46ae26b4e36f7b","tid":760893,"uid":162066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db8e8854fae43dbc6d94816ef8a3cc3a4b5c645b","tid":760893,"uid":59734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9715c15de756fcfb6b7caa29ba3b9f474bad54bb","tid":760893,"uid":162066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5afa100874e50ebcc0264134538b156f71aec545","tid":760893,"uid":59734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"想耐用D就研究下底版D  VRM 設計 唔好貪平<br />\n尤其用一體水又無風吹底板版heatsink"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"Small potato未玩過水冷，有必要上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:18:04.000Z","msg":"其實唔駛，不過要確保連塊版都要有風吹到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"唔該哂，咁list個塊板夠唔夠玩，要唔要直Z370"},{"pid":"6d91ac5a7e0ff86b23713edfa37e2fc8fa050179","tid":760893,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/175531_3201fc41ac52c6c53fdd7e737d04ae77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F175531_3201fc41ac52c6c53fdd7e737d04ae77.png&h=d9debf56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMHW 至少要 GTX 1060 至行到1080p 60fps <br />\n如果絲滑順暢 = 144hz<br />\n就可能要 GTX 1080至滿足到你<br />\n<br />\nMHW 有 SSD 會 load 得快好多<br />\n你睇吓PS4版啲巴打點講就明"},{"pid":"c7adc8ce07f1732d15704dd163658e255246024d","tid":760893,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"想知有幾多PS4用家真係會想LOAD快啲而轉咗用SSD<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/567336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/567336</a><br />\n<br />\n好多 MHW 玩家都表示換咗 SSD 之後 load 得快咗，相信PC版載入速度會更明顯。"},{"pid":"b3e3236ba8343ab840bdf0570051145914e02935","tid":760893,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟部機用左5年，差不多係時候換機<br />\n<br />\n換機既目標係想絲滑順暢咁打MHW同埋BF5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家個list大概就係 :<br />\n<br />\nCPU :  i7-8700<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">底板 :  B360 AORUS GAMING 3 WIFI</span></span><br />\ndisplay card : GTX1060 6GB (而家用緊)<br />\n火牛 : 550w (用緊)<br />\nHDD : ???<br />\n<br />\n想問下如果唔玩超頻，8700係咪抵玩過8700K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n底板個到，8700既話多數配B360,但B360都有成堆，唔識揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHHD有冇巴打可以推介D長壽唔易死既, 3TB夠玩了<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下SSD同RAM係電腦節先買會唔會抵買D？而家RAM價真係升得快過火箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該哂，咁多巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">技</span></span>"},{"pid":"f108d3ddf4d1a466a672f94643da244a7f1a4536","tid":760893,"uid":147026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:35:58.000Z","msg":"I7 8700唔超頻用stock fan都夠，但想好小小散較果就用CM 212塔式散熱，已經夠用有餘！用水冷唔值！<br />\n<br />\n底板對效能影響唔直接，但佢影響擴充性，例如可插幾多條Ram、support Ram幾多mhz超頻、有幾多lane俾Display card、PCIE、M.2、SATA用、有幾多個USB、有冇Wifi、甚至RGB等！<br />\n<br />\n基本上你唔係SLI、Ram超頻到3000Mhz、兩個M.2 SSD，五六隻HDD，又sound card、capture card，B360甚至H310都夠！假如真係要多點擴充性能，可考慮H370系列。<br />\n<br />\n但你話要好Smooth玩BF5同MHW，或之後嘅Game，就建議你上1070或以上！<br />\n<br />\n火牛就睇你用咗幾耐同咩牌子。550W基本夠，但如果用咗好耐就建議你換，另外，假如係GTR火牛，為保性命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，都換啦！"},{"pid":"2850ae8187a3455db4f1e8f5872f204c2a7dec32","tid":760893,"uid":162066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f108d3ddf4d1a466a672f94643da244a7f1a4536","tid":760893,"uid":147026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:35:58.000Z","msg":"I7 8700唔超頻用stock fan都夠，但想好小小散較果就用CM 212塔式散熱，已經夠用有餘！用水冷唔值！<br />\n<br />\n底板對效能影響唔直接，但佢影響擴充性，例如可插幾多條Ram、support Ram幾多mhz超頻、有幾多lane俾Display card、PCIE、M.2、SATA用、有幾多個USB、有冇Wifi、甚至RGB等！<br />\n<br />\n基本上你唔係SLI、Ram超頻到3000Mhz、兩個M.2 SSD，五六隻HDD，又sound card、capture card，B360甚至H310都夠！假如真係要多點擴充性能，可考慮H370系列。<br />\n<br />\n但你話要好Smooth玩BF5同MHW，或之後嘅Game，就建議你上1070或以上！<br />\n<br />\n火牛就睇你用咗幾耐同咩牌子。550W基本夠，但如果用咗好耐就建議你換，另外，假如係GTR火牛，為保性命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，都換啦！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:21:40.000Z","msg":"火牛Cooler Master唔會炸掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw, thx 巴打！"},{"pid":"ee16252aca3a4545cae92bf98618caeb464862f8","tid":760893,"uid":162066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3e3236ba8343ab840bdf0570051145914e02935","tid":760893,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟部機用左5年，差不多係時候換機<br />\n<br />\n換機既目標係想絲滑順暢咁打MHW同埋BF5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家個list大概就係 :<br />\n<br />\nCPU :  i7-8700<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">底板 :  B360 AORUS GAMING 3 WIFI</span></span><br />\ndisplay card : GTX1060 6GB (而家用緊)<br />\n火牛 